<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Booking Notification</title>
    <style>
        /* Add your custom styling here */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h2>New Booking Notification for {{serviceName}} on {{date}}</h2>

<p>Hello {{adminName}},</p>

<p>A new booking has been made. Below are the details:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Client Name:</strong> {{clientName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Service:</strong> {{serviceName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Staff Member:</strong> {{staffName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</li>
    <li><strong>Time:</strong> {{time}}</li>
    <li><strong>Total Amount:</strong> {{totalAmount}}</li>
    <li><strong>Status:</strong> {{status}}</li>
    <li><strong>Notes:</strong> {{notes}}</li>
</ul>

<p>If necessary, please take the required actions and ensure that the booking is appropriately handled.</p>

<p>Thank you!</p>

<p>Best Regards,<br>
    {{companyName}} Admin Team<br>
    {{adminMail}}</p>
</body>
</html>
